Take EE 16B. Math 54 will add nothing new to what you've learned in EE 16A. While EE 16B will hone your Lin alg skills more and teach you SVD and PCA (both very important in Data Analysis and Data Science). Also great ML prep as the above student answer mentions (since DS does require a ML class I believe?)
